    <item>
      <title>哈里斯-沃尔兹组合为爱荷华州民主党赢得席位带来希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/democrats-gain-hope-in-iowa-with-harris-walz-jolt-vilsack-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前农业州州长汤姆·维尔萨克表示，卡马拉·哈里斯和蒂姆·沃尔兹在最后一刻的总统竞选活动激发了民主党人的热情，这可能有助于该党赢得共和党据点爱荷华州的一些下级选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/democrats-gain-hope-in-iowa-with-harris-walz-jolt-vilsack-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>助手称哈里斯支持扩大加密行业的政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/harris-supports-policies-to-expand-crypto-industry-aide-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的竞选政策顾问表示，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将支持有助于发展数字资产的措施，并强调努力吸引新兴加密货币行业扩大其政治影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/harris-supports-policies-to-expand-crypto-industry-aide-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 18:38:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多呼吁铁路公司与工会达成协议避免罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/trudeau-calls-on-railways-union-to-reach-deal-to-stave-off-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多呼吁加拿大两大铁路公司和工会工人达成协议，避免罢工或停工，企业警告称，罢工或停工将对加拿大和美国经济造成重大损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/trudeau-calls-on-railways-union-to-reach-deal-to-stave-off-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:24:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美争夺支持 太平洋“大博弈”展开</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/new-great-game-unfolds-in-pacific-as-us-china-vie-for-backing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分布在太平洋上的岛国正处于中美两国为争夺海上航线、深水港和其他战略资产而展开的激烈竞争的中心，洛伊研究所称之为一场新的“大博弈”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/new-great-game-unfolds-in-pacific-as-us-china-vie-for-backing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
